race.comment: PRETTY PANAMA (2) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fifth (26.49) at Geelong latest. Solid record here winning eight races. Should bounce back. AGON CARAMEL (3) was among the minors three back at this track then missed the frame the last two, but drawn box 3 this time where she has two wins. Has the ability and expected to do much better. SARAH LOUISE (7) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish. Something for the Multiples: BLANK SLATE (4)
